SWORD members enrolled in the Virtual Physical Care program can:

Track progress: Stay motivated to complete your weekly goals
Chat with an expert: Message your Physical Health Specialist anytime, anywhere
Discover new content: Learn easy exercises you can do at home to prevent pain
See relevant content: Read topical articles about physical health and wellness

This app is a part of the SWORD Health ecosystem, so only SWORD members are able to fully access all features.

About SWORD
SWORD Health is the world’s fastest growing digital musculoskeletal (MSK) care provider, on a mission to free two billion people from acute, chronic, and post-surgical pain. It is the first digital solution to pair its members with a licensed physical therapist and the SWORD Health Digital Therapist to deliver a clinically-proven, personalized treatment plan that is more effective, easier, and less expensive than traditional in-person care. Learn more at www.swordhealth.com

title: Sword Health

creator: Sword Health
descriptionHtml:
Sword Health helps you recover from musculoskeletal (MSK) injuries, surgery, and muscle and joint pain with a personalized exercise program, a dedicated Physical Therapist, and a clinical care team by your side. 24/7 access to clinical support, and a variety of educational content including articles and videos, helps avoid future pain.
